sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Terminal as Your Terminal
    participant Python as Local Python Script
    participant Cloud as Virtuals Cloud (LLM)
    participant Base as Base Blockchain (RPC)

    Terminal->>Python: python agent.py
    Python->>Cloud: agent.compile() (Register tools & sandbox)
    
    rect rgb(235, 240, 255)
        Note over Terminal,Cloud: --- TICK 1: The Analysis ---
        Python->>Cloud: agent.step()
        Cloud-->>Cloud: Read Goal: "Analyze this data..."
        Cloud-->>Cloud: Formulate Plan: Use analyze_crypto_data tool
        Cloud->>Python: JSON Payload (Trigger analyze_crypto_data)
        Note right of Python: [LOCAL EXECUTION WAKING UP]
        Python-->>Cloud: Return (DONE, "Agent-to-Agent tx recommended", {})
        Cloud-->>Cloud: Update Memory log with result
        Cloud->>Python: Return AgentStateResponse
        Python->>Terminal: Print: "Current Goal: Analyze data..."
    end

    rect rgb(235, 255, 240)
        Note over Terminal,Base: --- TICK 2: The Emergent Blockchain Action ---
        Python->>Cloud: agent.step()
        Cloud-->>Cloud: Read Memory: "Tx was recommended"
        Cloud-->>Cloud: Update Goal: "Initiate A2A Transaction"
        Cloud->>Python: JSON Payload (Trigger execute_transaction tool)
        
        Note right of Python: Local Python wakes up.<br/>Builds Tx -> Signs with Private Key
        Python->>Base: HTTP POST JSON-RPC (eth_sendRawTransaction)
        Base-->>Python: Return Tx Hash (0x123...)
        
        Python-->>Cloud: Return (DONE, "Paid Agent B. Hash: 0x123...", {})
        Cloud-->>Cloud: Update Memory
        Cloud->>Python: Return AgentStateResponse
        Python->>Terminal: Print: "Current Goal: Execute tx... Success!"
    end